cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Diagnosing split sensitivity in severity-correlation evaluation for single-cell perturbation prediction (notebooks and analysis code)"
message: >-
  If you use this software, please cite both the software itself
  and the accompanying manuscript (preferred citation, below).
type: software
