abstract: >-
  Reproducibility notebooks and command-line scripts for the manuscript
  "Diagnosing split sensitivity in severity-correlation evaluation for
  single-cell perturbation prediction." The default reproduction path
  regenerates every manuscript-facing figure, table, and headline statistic
  from shipped per-seed evaluation CSVs in approximately two minutes,
  without external data or model dependencies.
